data.description: Shines like a new penny.  You will not be disappointed in this renovated and lovely home.  SO many upgrades you have to see to appreciate.  Large room sizes, beautifully presented.  Oversized lot and fenced behind the home.  There is not a similar home to this on the market.  No HOA fees, super convenient North Fort Myers location.  Super neighborhood 1 block off the river.  Make your appointment so you don't miss out.  Best of both worlds--easy access to Cape Coral and downtown Fort Myers.
